    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><date>Monday</date> Morning</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <date>Jany 23/60</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev I Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I think it<lb/> due to myself as well as your-<lb/>self that I
                should give you<lb/> an extract of a letter I re-<lb/>ceived last
                        <date><sic>friday</sic></date> from <persName>Dr Mayer</persName><lb/> “upon
                expressing my astonish-<lb/>ment to <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> that you a<lb/>
                staunch orthodox should<lb/> have applied for a situation<lb/> as minister to a
                reformed<lb/> congregation he at once and<lb/> very curtly observed He'll do<lb/>
                anything for money. It was in<lb/> that conversation he told me that<lb/> a Hebrew
                lady of <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> upon<lb/> one occasion of his calling
                just<lb/> when you left her house, had<lb/> requested him to tell you that<lb/> she
                wished to dispense with<lb/> your visits for the reason</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>as assigned by <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> be-<lb/>cause you called too often<lb/>
                and protracted your visits too<lb/> long. He also told me then that<lb/>
                <persName>Dr Fischel</persName> had related to him the<lb/> fact of your intended
                conversion.<lb/> The tone of <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> during<lb/> the whole
                conversation was that<lb/> of indignation and contempt<lb/> produced as then was and
                is<lb/> still my impression. I say this<lb/> injustice to him, by his belief,
                that<lb/> you had deceived him with<lb/> regard to your profession of<lb/>
                orthodoxy.”</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">I am</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">Your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">Abraham Harris</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <placeName>Charleston S.C.</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
